title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Using simBrief with Working Title CJ4
description:
In this how to we are going to look at how to plan a flight using simBrief and load it directly into our airplane using the Working Title CJ4 addon for Microsoft Flight Simulator 2020.

Working Title CJ4 can be downloaded from this site: https://github.com/Working-Title-MSFS-Mods/fspackages

The tool used to plan our flight simBrief can be found here: https://www.simbrief.com
